" />"},{"pid":"85927f33c8ce0f8cb0d0d1f67ea67dcbadbecd44","tid":2168453,"uid":150293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3420de2439162bb1f7993efb186a8da77e3754e","tid":2168453,"uid":302374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f00eaf600f604432867a50e3e7e3513dac24d4ba","tid":2168453,"uid":150293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83e4955eb3b7095ca3f86369386ab380f19d8a0d","tid":2168453,"uid":302374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T19:27:42.000Z","msg":"下我唔係講緊我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇清楚D先唔好衝出黎柒啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T19:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我睇錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T19:31:05.000Z","msg":"但就算比佢地入到大學又點<br />\n而家d樓咁貴<br />\n邊到住得起<br />\n唉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T19:37:00.000Z","msg":"你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好想買樓<br />\n發下夢好了"},{"pid":"54b58a68323353f2bdc1690f96e8ddec6a2081b0","tid":2168453,"uid":303524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T19:38:58.000Z","msg":"咁講啦 窮都有分好彩同唔好彩既。知道自己屋企窮,但願意盡自己力去養仔女既，其實都可以生。又窮又冇遠見唔願意好好養育仔女既先至唔好生。<br />\n<br />\n利申屋企頗窮，但父母對我好，好既都會比咗我先，將來一定會報答。"}]}